<div class="row">

	<div class="col-md-3">
		<div class="list-group">
			<div data-clampedwidth=".col-md-3" id="controlsWrapper">
				<a id="loadingMap" class="list-group-item">
					<h4 class="list-group-item-header">
						<img src="img/ajax-loader.gif" /> Loading map...&hellip;
					</h4>
				</a>
				<a id="mapControls" class="list-group-item active" style="display: none"></a>
				<a id="concentrationGraphControls" class="list-group-item" style="display: none">
					<h4 class="list-group-item-header">Graph</h4>
					<p></p>
				</a>
				<a id="thresholdGraphicControls" class="list-group-item" style="display: none">
					<h4 class="list-group-item-header">Visualization</h4>
					<p>Ice coverage by % threshold</p>
				</a>
				<a id="mapAnimationControls" class="list-group-item" style="display: none"></a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!--start 9-column map block-->
	<div class="col-md-9">
		<div id="mapGroupWrapper">
			<div id="animationBuffering" style="display: none" class="panel panel-info">
				<h4><img src="img/ajax-loader.gif" /> Loading map data&hellip;</h4>
			</div>
			<h3 id="mapTitle">Historical Sea Ice Concentration</h3>
			<div id="mapWrapper">
				<div id="map" style="height: 650px"></div>
				<img id="legend" src="img/legend2.png" />
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="chartWrapper" style="display: none">
			<h4>Average monthly sea ice concentrations for all years</h4>
				<p>Percent ice cover for your chosen month at your location.
				Use &ldquo;select by date&rdquo; at upper left to choose another month.</p>

			<button class="btn btn-primary btn-xs" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#chartModalInfo">
			  More information&hellip;
			</button>

			<div class="modal fade" id="chartModalInfo" tabindex="-1">
				<div class="modal-dialog">
					<div class="modal-content">
						<div class="modal-header">
							<button class="close" data-dismiss="modal"type="button">x</button>
							<h4 class="modal-title" id="chartModalInfoLabel">Average monthly sea ice concentrations for all years</h4>
						</div>
						<div class="modal-body">
							<p>This graph shows sea ice concentrations
							(percent ice cover) for your chosen month at
							the location you clicked on the map. Use the
							&ldquo;select by date&rdquo; menu at upper left to choose
							another month to view. No need to change the
							year because you are already viewing the entire
							time series of data.</p>
							<p><a href="/glossary.jade">Learn more about
							how sea ice concentrations are defined and
							described.</a></p>
						</div>
						<div class="modal-footer">
							<button class="btn btn-default btn-sm" data-dismiss="modal" type="button">Got it!</button>
						</div>
					</div><!-- /.modal-content -->
				</div><!-- /.modal-dialog -->
			</div><!-- /.modal -->

			<div id="chart"></div>
		</div>
		<div id="graphicWrapper" style="display: none">
			<h4>Open water over time (gray bars = ice cover)</h4>

			<p>Sea ice concentrations for the entire time series at your
			location. Use the slider-bar control to change the minimum
			threshold.  <button id="chartModalInfoButton2" class="btn btn-primary btn-xs" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#chartModalInfo2"> More information&hellip; </button>  </p>



				<div class="modal fade" id="chartModalInfo2" tabindex="-1">
					<div class="modal-dialog">
						<div class="modal-content">
							<div class="modal-header">
								<button class="close" data-dismiss="modal"
								type="button">Ã—</button>

								<h4 class="modal-title" id="chartModalInfo2Label">Open water for all years (gray bars = ice over)</h4>
							</div>

							<div class="modal-body">
								<p>This graph shows historical sea ice
								concentrations (percent ice cover) for the
								entire time series at the point you clicked on
								the map. The gray bars initially show ice cover
								that exceeds the default threshold
								concentration of 30% for your location. Move
								the blue dot on the slider bar below to make
								the chart show where the ice concentration
								exceeds your selected threshold.</p>

								<p><a href="/glossary.jade">Learn more about
								how sea ice concentrations are defined and
								described.</a></p>
							</div>

							<div class="modal-footer">
								<button class="btn btn-default btn-sm" data-dismiss="modal" type="button">Got it!</utton>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			<div>
				<input id="thresholdSlider" type="text" data-slider-id="thresholdSliderControl" data-slider-min="1" data-slider-max="100" data-slider-step="1" data-slider-value="30"/>
	      			<span>&nbsp;Threshold: <span id="thresholdSliderLabel">30</span>&#37;</span>
      			</div>
      			<div id="thresholdTarget"></div>
			<div id="openWaterGraphic"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
